00:16:20.940 --> 00:16:22.660
Tú, yo...

00:16:23.300 --> 00:16:24.140
Te digo,

00:16:24.300 --> 00:16:26.180
te considero a mi amiga.

00:16:26.860 --> 00:16:27.380
No hay problema.

00:16:31.860 --> 00:16:32.740
Adiós.

