00:16:42.180 --> 00:16:42.540
Vamos.

00:16:42.540 --> 00:16:43.420
No voy.

00:16:43.780 --> 00:16:45.260
Voy a la cabaña del bosque.

00:16:45.370 --> 00:16:46.780
